Stopped fishing chinook in the rivers 6 years ago due to stuff like this.  Snaggers can have the creeks, I'll stick to the piers.
Fifteen years or so for me.  I gave up Lake O tribs when a guy with a sword ran by me in the river chasing a nook.  Yes, a sword.
the video was removed he probably figured someone finds the spot or that they see how many fish he took
